parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Engine Failure and Oil Consumption Issues
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the engine can cause the vehicle to stall, lose power, and potentially lead to accidents, injuries, or fatalities. Excessive oil consumption can lead to engine failure, which can cause the vehicle to stall or catch fire.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or loses power
loud knocking or ticking sounds from the engine
excessive oil consumption
engine warning lights illuminate
difficulty starting the engine
and loss of motive power.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Engine Stalling and Loss of Power
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The stalling of the engine can cause the vehicle to lose power, which can lead to accidents, injuries, or fatalities, especially if the vehicle is traveling at high speeds.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or loses power
difficulty starting the engine
loss of motive power
and engine warning lights illuminate.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Excessive oil consumption can lead to engine failure, which can cause the vehicle to stall or catch fire, potentially leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: Excessive oil consumption
engine warning lights illuminate
loud knocking or ticking sounds from the engine
and difficulty starting the engine.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delay in repairing recalled vehicles can lead to continued use of potentially dangerous vehicles, which can cause accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: Parts are not available for recall repairs
dealerships are unable to diagnose or repair the issue
and manufacturers are not providing timely assistance.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission failure and unpredictable behavior can cause the vehicle to stall, jerk, or lunge forward, leading to accidents or near-misses, especially when braking or accelerating.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or dies when coming to a stop
jerks or lunges forward when accelerating
has delayed transmission engagement
makes a winding noise
has no power to move forward
has difficulty shifting gears
and has a loud grinding noise.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning blind spot warning system can cause the driver to be unaware of vehicles in the blind spot, leading to potential accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: The blind spot warning lights turn on even when there are no vehicles in the blind spot.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Low Tire Pressure Warning System Malfunction
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning low tire pressure warning system can cause the driver to be unaware of underinflated tires, leading to potential accidents or tire blowouts.
symptoms: The low tire pressure warning light turns on even when the tires are properly inflated.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission control system failure can cause the vehicle to stall, jerk, or lunge forward, leading to accidents or near-misses, especially when braking or accelerating.
symptoms: The vehicle displays a message on the car information screen indicating a possible condition with the transmission control system
and a full system check is recommended.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the horn can increase the risk of accidents, as it is an essential safety feature for alerting other drivers and pedestrians.
symptoms: The horn stops working
resulting in close calls with other vehicles and pedestrians.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The acceleration problems can lead to accidents, as the vehicle may not respond as expected, causing the driver to lose control.
symptoms: The vehicle hesitates or bucks when accelerating
the tachometer moves to higher levels but the car doesn't accelerate
the car stalls or hesitates when starting from a cold start.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The defective oil rings can cause engine failure, leading to accidents, fires, and injuries.
symptoms: The engine may run badly
causing it to lock up and throw a rod
potentially leading to a fire.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission slippage can cause the vehicle to move unexpectedly, leading to accidents and injuries.
symptoms: The transmission slips out of park
causing the vehicle to roll or move unexpectedly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The defective headlights can compromise the driver's visibility, increasing the risk of accidents, especially at night.
symptoms: The headlights get full of condensation
obstructing the light and road ahead
and may turn off and on unexpectedly.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Transmission Damage due to Spare Tire Use
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission damage can cause the vehicle to malfunction, leading to accidents and injuries.
symptoms: The transmission fluid is burned
and metal shavings are present
causing the transmission to fail.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The engine compartment fire can cause significant damage to the vehicle, potentially leading to a total loss, and poses a risk to the safety of occupants and other road users.
symptoms: The vehicle catches on fire while parked and unoccupied
with no warning lights illuminated before the incident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning blind spot warning system can cause unnecessary alerts, distracting the driver and potentially leading to accidents.
symptoms: The blind spot monitor lights up and beeps at random times
even when there is nothing in the blind spot.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The automatic downshifting and lurching can cause loss of control, accidents, or near-misses, posing a risk to the safety of occupants and other road users.
symptoms: The vehicle automatically downshifts
causing the vehicle to lurch
especially on rural two-way roads.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Sudden Loss of Motive Power and Stalling
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden loss of motive power and stalling can cause accidents, especially if the vehicle stalls in traffic, and can leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle suddenly loses motive power and stalls
often while driving at various speeds
and may restart normally after a short period.
